#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:1 of
msgid "Modified Bessel function of the first kind of real order."
msgstr "实数阶的第一类修正贝塞尔函数。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.iv.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:3 of
msgid "Order. If `z` is of real type and negative, `v` must be integer valued."
msgstr "阶数。如果 `z` 是实数类型且为负数，则 `v` 必须是整数值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:6 of
msgid "Argument."
msgstr "自变量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:8 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "可选的输出数组，用于存储函数值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.iv.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:11 of
msgid "Values of the modified Bessel function."
msgstr "修正贝塞尔函数的值。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.iv.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:16 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ive`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:17 of
msgid "This function with leading exponential behavior stripped off."
msgstr "去除主导指数行为后的该函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`i0`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:20 of
msgid "Faster version of this function for order 0."
msgstr "阶数为0时的快速版本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`i1`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:23 of
msgid "Faster version of this function for order 1."
msgstr "阶数为1时的快速版本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:27 of
msgid ""
"For real `z` and :math:`v \\in [-50, 50]`, the evaluation is carried out "
"using Temme's method [1]_.  For larger orders, uniform asymptotic "
"expansions are applied."
msgstr ""
"对于实数 `z` 和 :math:`v \\in [-50, 50]`，使用 Temme 方法 [1]_ 进行计算。"
"对于更大的阶数，采用一致渐近展开式。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:31 of
msgid ""
"For complex `z` and positive `v`, the AMOS [2]_ `zbesi` routine is "
"called. It uses a power series for small `z`, the asymptotic expansion "
"for large `abs(z)`, the Miller algorithm normalized by the Wronskian and "
"a Neumann series for intermediate magnitudes, and the uniform asymptotic "
"expansions for :math:`I_v(z)` and :math:`J_v(z)` for large orders. "
"Backward recurrence is used to generate sequences or reduce orders when "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
"对于复数 `z` 和正数 `v`，调用 AMOS [2]_ 的 `zbesi` 例程。它对小 `z` 使用"
"幂级数，对大的 `abs(z)` 使用渐近展开式，对中等大小的值使用由 Wronskian "
"归一化的 Miller 算法和 Neumann 级数，对大阶数使用 :math:`I_v(z)` 和 :math"
":`J_v(z)` 的一致渐近展开式。在必要时使用向后递推生成序列或降低阶数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:39 of
msgid ""
"The calculations above are done in the right half plane and continued "
"into the left half plane by the formula,"
msgstr "上述计算在右半平面进行，并通过以下公式延拓到左半平面，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:42 of
msgid ""
"I_v(z \\exp(\\pm\\imath\\pi)) = \\exp(\\pm\\pi v) I_v(z)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:44 of
msgid ""
"(valid when the real part of `z` is positive).  For negative `v`, the "
"formula"
msgstr "（当 `z` 的实部为正时有效）。对于负 `v`，使用以下公式"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:47 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"I_{-v}(z) = I_v(z) + \\frac{2}{\\pi} \\sin(\\pi v) K_v(z)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:49 of
msgid ""
"is used, where :math:`K_v(z)` is the modified Bessel function of the "
"second kind, evaluated using the AMOS routine `zbesk`."
msgstr "其中 :math:`K_v(z)` 是第二类修正贝塞尔函数，使用 AMOS 例程 `zbesk` 计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.iv:53 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

